    binary interaction parameters).  Choupo does NOT include, link, or
    redistribute ChemSep SIMULATOR source code.

Place the canonical licence text next to this NOTICE as:
    thirdParty/chemsep/pcd/Artistic_license_2_0.txt
(use the copy that ships WITH the ChemSep download, or the canonical text from
https://opensource.org/license/artistic-2-0 -- do not paraphrase a licence).

Every value imported into Choupo from these files carries per-value provenance
(origin = ChemSep, authors, licence, source file/record) and is STAGED in
data/proposed/ for human review -- nothing is silently promoted to
data/standards/.
